data.description: Super cute two bedroom, one bath home right in the heart of Buna. Close to town but still in a very quiet grown-in neighborhood. This property has a HUGE shop, plus a 3 car carport for all those toys and tools! The property has large shade trees and an oversized concrete driveway. The property and home have never flooded, lot sits highest on the street per seller! Home is well maintained and ready for its new owner. Perfect starter home or even a bachelor pad! Call your agent today, this one has it all!
